org.modelio.vcore.smkernel.mapi

Interface MVisitor

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAbstractArchimateVisitor, IAbstractInfrastructureVisitor, IAbstractModelVisitor, IArchimateVisitor, IDefaultArchimateVisitor, IDefaultInfrastructureVisitor, IDefaultModelVisitor, IInfrastructureVisitor, IModelVisitor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractArchimateVisitor, AbstractInfrastructureVisitor, AbstractModelVisitor, CompositionInitializer, DefaultArchimateVisitor, DefaultInfrastructureVisitor, DefaultModelVisitor

    public interface MVisitor
    Acyclic Visitor design pattern applied to MObject.

    The Acyclic Visitor pattern allows new functions to be added to existing class hierarchies without affecting those hierarchies, and without creating the dependency cycles that are inherent to the GangOfFour VisitorPattern

    See Also:
    http://c2.com/cgi/wiki?AcyclicVisitor
